{"tid":1528101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"渡輪尾班船時間","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:18:48.000Z","uid":74091,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2caff017d8259265e3ec138792de5e2805ff24","tid":1528101,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"星期日天氣幾好，好多人搭船去離島玩，可以留意尾班船時間<br />\n<strong>星期日及公眾假期尾班船時間</strong> (大部份都11:30，唔知今日會唔會有特別安排)<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;愉景灣<br />\n由中環開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n由愉景灣開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;梅窩<br />\n由中環開出 11.40 p.m.<br />\n由梅窩開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;長洲<br />\n由中環開出 11.55 p.m<br />\n由長洲開出 11.30 p.m<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;坪洲 <br />\n由中環開出 11.40 p.m.<br />\n由坪洲開出 11.35 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;榕樹灣<br />\n由中環開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n由榕樹灣開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n中環&mdash;索罟灣<br />\n由中環開出 11.30 p.m.<br />\n由索罟灣開出 10.40 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n愉景灣&mdash;梅窩<br />\n由愉景灣開出 8.05 p.m.<br />\n由梅窩開出 8.30 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n馬灣&mdash;中環<br />\n由馬灣開出 11:00 p.m.<br />\n由中環開出 11:30 p.m.<br />\n<br />\n其他未有提及可在下面link搵下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/public_transport/ferries/service_details/index.html#o02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftransport_in_hong_kong%2Fpublic_transport%2Fferries%2Fservice_details%2Findex.html%23o02&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702GyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=13658266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/transport_in_hong_kong/public_transport/ferries/service_details/index.html#o02</a><br />\n<br />\n如果地面太多狗隻，怕比咬，建議同同行既人一齊借番間房住，第日睇情況走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記住安全先係第一</span></strong>"},{"pid":"84057a66ae380c1d32c18b726b6c36eecbab475f","tid":1528101,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"